News of the brutal killing of well-known South African rapper Kiernan Forbes, known as AKA, and his long-time friend Tebello ‘Tibz’ Motsoane has shocked many. A team of detectives of the police’s organised crime unit has taken over the investigation after two gunmen allegedly walked up to AKA and shot him and Motsoane outside a restaurant in a popular Durban nightlife district on Friday night. The police say the motive for the attack is not yet known. 